## Phase 1: Supabase Setup + Email Magic Link Authentication

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is the foundation. Every other feature (Chat History, per-user sessions) depends on having authenticated users. Must be built first.

### Auth Method: Email Magic Link (Passwordless)
- Engineer enters their email on the login page
- Supabase sends a one-time login link to their inbox
- Engineer clicks the link → automatically logged in (no password needed)
- Session stays active for 7 days before requiring re-authentication

### New Dependencies
```bash
npm install @supabase/supabase-js @supabase/ssr
```

### Supabase Schema
```sql
-- Users are managed by Supabase Auth automatically

-- Chat sessions table
CREATE TABLE chat_sessions (
  id UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  title TEXT,
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
);

-- Chat messages table
CREATE TABLE chat_messages (
  id UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id UUID REFERENCES chat_sessions(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  role TEXT CHECK (role IN ('user', 'assistant')),
  content TEXT NOT NULL,
  language TEXT DEFAULT 'en',
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
);
```

### File Changes
| Action | File | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| NEW | `lib/supabase/client.ts` | Browser-side Supabase client |
| NEW | `lib/supabase/server.ts` | Server-side Supabase client (for API routes) |
| NEW | `app/login/page.tsx` | Login page with "Enter email" form + "Send Magic Link" button |
| NEW | `app/login/check-email/page.tsx` | "Check your inbox" confirmation page |
| NEW | `app/auth/callback/route.ts` | Handles the magic link redirect, exchanges token for session |
| NEW | `middleware.ts` | Protects all routes except `/login` — redirects unauthenticated users |
| MODIFY | [app/layout.tsx](file:///d:/Ganesh/Office/Personal%20AI%20Agent/app/layout.tsx) | Wrap app in Supabase session provider |
| MODIFY | [app/page.tsx](file:///d:/Ganesh/Office/Personal%20AI%20Agent/app/page.tsx) | Show user email in header, add logout button |

### Environment Variables
```
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_url
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_anon_key
```

