## Phase 2: Chat History

### File Changes
| Action | File | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| NEW | `app/api/history/route.ts` | API to save/fetch chat messages from Supabase |
| NEW | `components/Sidebar.tsx` | Left sidebar showing past chat sessions |
| NEW | `app/chat/[sessionId]/page.tsx` | Dynamic route to load a specific past session |
| MODIFY | [app/api/chat/route.ts](file:///d:/Ganesh/Office/Personal%20AI%20Agent/app/api/chat/route.ts) | After streaming response, save both user message and AI response to Supabase |
| MODIFY | [app/page.tsx](file:///d:/Ganesh/Office/Personal%20AI%20Agent/app/page.tsx) | Add sidebar toggle, "New Chat" button, session list |

### Data Flow
1. User sends message → save to `chat_messages` with `role: 'user'`
2. AI generates response → save to `chat_messages` with `role: 'assistant'`
3. Sidebar queries `chat_sessions` for the logged-in user
4. Clicking a session loads its `chat_messages` ordered by `created_at`

