## Phase 5: Image Solution

### File Changes
| Action | File | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| NEW | `app/api/analyze-image/route.ts` | Accepts image upload, sends to vision model (Gemini 1.5 Pro Vision or GPT-4o), returns analysis |
| NEW | `components/ImageUpload.tsx` | Drag-and-drop or camera capture UI component |
| MODIFY | [app/page.tsx](file:///d:/Ganesh/Office/Personal%20AI%20Agent/app/page.tsx) | Add 📷 button next to input. Display uploaded image in chat bubble. |

### Architecture
Since Sarvam does not offer a Vision model, we will use **Google Gemini 1.5 Pro** (which you already have a key for) to analyze uploaded panel images, error codes, and wiring photos.

