## Verification Plan

### Per-Phase Testing
| Phase | Test |
|---|---|
| 1. Auth | Register → Login → Access chat → Logout → Verify redirect to login |
| 2. History | Send 3 messages → Refresh page → Verify messages persist in sidebar |
| 3. Translation | Select Hindi → Ask question → Verify Hindi response. Switch to Tamil → Verify Tamil response |
| 4. Voice | Press mic → Speak → Verify text appears → Verify audio plays back |
| 5. Image | Upload panel photo → Verify AI describes the issue and provides troubleshooting steps |
